{"task":"transcribe","language":"english","duration":37.66999816894531,"text":"Hey guys, my name is Nate. Today I wanted to talk to you about the golden ratio of AI automation, which basically means when you think of automating a process with AI, you think about the first 60% being automated with just deterministic logic, the next 30% being automated with AI, sort of AI assisted, and then that last 10% being kind of the human in the loop manual approval stage. And the reason why I think this is important is because some people think that AI is magic and it can do it all. Some people think that AI is trash and it can't do anything because they've only been using Copilot and really it's actually somewhere in the middle. So that's what I want to talk about in this video.","segments":[{"id":0,"seek":0,"start":0.8600000143051147,"end":2.299999952316284,"text":" Hey guys, my name is Nate.","tokens":[50364,1911,1074,11,452,1315,307,28064,13,50497],"temperature":0.0,"avg_logprob":-0.2298601269721985,"compression_ratio":1.7231833934783936,"no_speech_prob":0.16642411053180695},{"id":1,"seek":0,"start":2.640000104904175,"end":7.800000190734863,"text":" Today I wanted to talk to you about the golden ratio of AI automation, which basically means","tokens":[50497,2692,286,1415,281,751,281,291,466,264,9729,8509,295,7318,17769,11,597,1936,1355,50784],"temperature":0.0,"avg_logprob":-0.2298601269721985,"compression_ratio":1.7231833934783936,"no_speech_prob":0.16642411053180695},{"id":2,"seek":0,"start":8.199999809265137,"end":13.079999923706055,"text":" when you think of automating a process with AI, you think about the first 60% being automated","tokens":[50784,562,291,519,295,3553,990,257,1399,365,7318,11,291,519,466,264,700,4060,4,885,18473,51019],"temperature":0.0,"avg_logprob":-0.2298601269721985,"compression_ratio":1.7231833934783936,"no_speech_prob":0.16642411053180695},{"id":3,"seek":0,"start":13.420000076293945,"end":18.5,"text":" with just deterministic logic, the next 30%